    <div>
    <head>The Day-Breakers</head>
<lg>
    <l>We are not come to wage a strife</l>
    <l>With swords upon this hill,</l>
    <l>It is not wise to waste the life</l>
    <l>Against a stubborn will.</l>
    <l>Yet would we die as some have done.</l>
    <l>Beating a way for the rising sun.</l>
</lg>
<byline>-Arna Bontemps</byline>
        </div>
